Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在在你眼前有著無限的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海底兩萬哩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭懦弱的人無法背叛藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在作夢之前我想翱翔天際
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心中的音樂盒開啟發出聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點一滴演奏出幸福與勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:01:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在在你眼前有著無限的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,言語是永遠的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛比寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#39星之繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你﹐對娜蒂亞開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過﹐你狠得下心\N對娜蒂亞開槍嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞﹐快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是用你愛的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞公主的意識\N已經喚不回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱持著寬大的慈悲心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再給你一次活下去的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意以\N亞特蘭提斯人之王的身分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,協助我們將愚蠢的人類\N帶往正途嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答案還是跟13年前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒清醒過來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:03:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勸你別太小看人類﹐石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類並不如你所想的那麼愚昧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不認為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像那名少年\N就無法對娜蒂亞開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了達成目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他應該毫不猶豫\N扣下扳機才對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那才是人類的善良之處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他們的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不﹐那是不需要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是時候讓你消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前先讓你聽聽\N你親生兒子的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我以友人身分送給你的\N最後一個禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼那西斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾乃新亞特蘭提斯帝國皇帝\N尼歐‧伊肯‧艾皮法尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石像鬼﹐難不成均KA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猜對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:04:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你兒子現在不過是我的\N扯線木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼歐、娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對尼莫開槍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船長！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被自己的孩子殺死\N是什麼感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你將會死在自己孩子的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我這位好友的一點心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新鸚鵡螺號﹐聽到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新鸚鵡螺號﹐聽到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是﹐這裡是鸚鵡螺號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副船長﹐妳平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曉得我的位置嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是﹐追蹤得到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將座標往左偏移60\N發射電子砲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運氣好的話就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去只會坐以待斃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請發射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然船長就要被殺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊？尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成果很不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們新亞特蘭提斯的\N科學結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是…科學？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的肉體早在13年前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就被尼莫\N和巴別塔一起四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有我藉由科學的力量救了他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此讓你的兒子多活了13年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得自己應該受人感謝\N而不是怨恨才對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會遭到主砲直接攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的遺跡戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然刻意瞄準尼歐的控制裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父王？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…不可能會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼歐的意識\N明明就已經徹底消除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在竟然又恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這簡直是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞﹐快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非破壞控制裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則娜蒂亞不可能清醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了是誰將我的身體\N改造成金屬的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼那西斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼歐﹐你不過是個機器娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電源一斷只能落得這種下場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇蹟就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你連一根手指頭都動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就直接下黃泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此不合乎科學的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道人的意志力\N真的足以超越科學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼那西斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起﹐娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我也能跟人類一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是愚蠢傢伙的下場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬧劇就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去會直接衝入大氣圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是紅色諾亞\N以這樣的角度根本…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法﹐只好硬幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今尼歐皇帝已經逝世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔚藍之水的繼承人就是妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你殺死他的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他已經沒有用處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就處分掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞公主\N請妳將蔚藍之水復原
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並將這艘船導回正確軌道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不在乎他們的死活嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身為蔚藍之水的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定要毀滅這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯﹐娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不需要擔心我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新鸚鵡螺號一定會來救我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候我們就一起回地球去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還是一樣那麼勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然不知珍惜自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以為凡事都能隨意掌控的你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是人心可不像機機一樣\N能隨你任意操弄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸和哥哥\N都不惜為了自己的信念犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也繼承他們的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你稱心如意的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就難說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我勉強饒了她一命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下妳願意讓蔚藍之水復原了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是採取合理的手段\N以求達到目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧﹐娜蒂亞公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳就看看心上人的屍體\N再來後悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遺跡戰艦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強！強！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你﹐回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這個拿去用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向兩顆蔚藍之水許願
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔚藍之水一定會回應妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果沒有蔚藍之水\N你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用不著擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳是個女人\N就該優先救自己心上人的命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人就該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔚藍之水將會永遠失去光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行﹐快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望之光…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能在那道光芒中存活下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有亞特蘭提斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼會變成鹽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世上的亞特蘭提斯人\N現在只剩下兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涅墨西斯‧拉‧阿爾果\N你是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我至今所做的一切不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟娜蒂亞兩個外星人\N又能做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個星球已經是人類的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰將我從沉睡中喚醒的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是娜蒂亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的﹐拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳…請妳救救強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他的生命已經走到盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是尼莫船長說妳可以救他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求妳﹐救救強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這麼一來\N妳將會失去蔚藍之水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去妳因為身為亞特蘭提斯人\N而被賦予的一切力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是放棄成為神的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不需要那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳…請妳救救強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這顆石頭是\N亞特蘭提斯人靈魂的延續
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就將我們的生命獻給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了﹐娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強﹐太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船長﹐尼莫船長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:19:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事﹐全員立刻登艦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舷穩定器受損
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎輸出動力降至0.2%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行﹐根本動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡﹐沒救了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以說洩氣話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定要活著回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不﹐還有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與新鸚鵡螺號連接電源
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始填充能源
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離啟動可能時間還有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫船長呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會用新鸚鵡螺號破壞發射口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為你們開出一條活路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個父親能為妳做的\N就只有這麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要﹐我也要留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要跟爸爸一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算我求妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求妳體諒他的苦心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛蘭迪絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們就拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不﹐梅蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後的事就拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論遇到什麼困難
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳都要活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.90,0:23:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.07,0:23:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在太空船裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太空船？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.47,0:23:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對﹐我們即將返回你的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說錯了﹐娜蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的故鄉才對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.69,0:23:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是妳出生的星球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.09,0:23:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一樣都是地球人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.17,0:23:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是流星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.54,0:23:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉許了什麼願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:24:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望桑森還有大家\N能早點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.22,0:24:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望以後不要再發生同樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.40,0:24:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.47,0:24:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（全劇終）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.65,0:24:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個故事到此全部結束
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.09,0:24:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來向各位報告一些\N之後的情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.26,0:24:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後已經過了12年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.26,0:24:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的鸚鵡螺號\N沉入了日本海溝深處
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.27,0:24:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船員們現在都過著各自的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.74,0:24:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾科哥哥和護士姊姊\N在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.54,0:25:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗朵拉則是聽說\N一心一意將孩子撫養長大
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.34,0:25:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強與娜蒂亞終於在5年前結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.85,0:25:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前定居勒阿弗爾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.02,0:25:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說強現在也還是一樣\N和他的姑丈埋頭發明
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.76,0:25:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害得娜蒂亞與姑姑\N總是有發不完的牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.83,0:25:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亞雖然已經當了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.70,0:25:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻還是一樣不肯吃魚跟肉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.00,0:25:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.24,0:25:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛蘭迪絲至今好像還是一個人\N享受著自由自在的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.11,0:25:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會永遠追求\N屬於自己的愛情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.32,0:25:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韓森開了間汽車公司
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.15,0:25:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成了我們之中最有錢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.92,0:25:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我就只差一位漂亮老婆了”
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.99,0:25:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次見面時他這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.03,0:25:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾爾頓聽說回到英國\N乖乖繼承家業
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.20,0:25:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來他真的是位伯爵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.57,0:26:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑森過得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.67,0:26:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.61,0:26:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在是我\N瑪莉‧安‧雷溫佛洛伊的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.48,0:26:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而明年我就要跟娜蒂亞一樣\N當媽媽了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.12,0:26:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的夢想就是在星期天\N全家人一起到附近的公園散步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.40,0:26:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼﹐後會有期囉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.17,0:26:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼應付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.18,0:26:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要看不清遠方的夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.25,0:26:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喃喃自語仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.66,0:27:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與你的約定耀眼閃爍著
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.50,0:27:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try安慰的話語\N是傳達不到內心的風
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.64,0:27:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然背負的不安逐漸膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.52,0:27:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這是我自己的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.69,0:27:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人應該也不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.39,0:27:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使跌倒或感到迷惘\N仍然有明天
